'''廣播大樓'''（Broadcasting House）是[[BBC威爾斯|BBC威爾斯]]的總部，位於[[威爾斯|威爾斯]]首府[[卡地夫|卡地夫]]北部。這座建築開業於1966年，由攝影棚、辦公區和技術設施三個部分構成<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/info/ |title=Nations – Wales – BBC Cymru Wales |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2013-09-17 |archive-date=2013-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130117045459/http://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/info/ }}</ref>。2015年，BBC宣布將把總部遷往位於[[加迪夫中央車站|加迪夫中央車站]]北側的中央廣場<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.walesonline.co.uk/business/business-news/new-headquarters-bbc-cymru-wales-10358925 |title= New headquarters for BBC Cymru Wales expected to be confirmed shortly at heart of Central Square scheme |publisher= [[Wales_Online|Wales Online]] |date= 30 November 2015 |accessdate= 16 November 2015 |archive-date= 2021-01-17 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210117093129/https://www.walesonline.co.uk/business/business-news/new-headquarters-bbc-cymru-wales-10358925 }}</ref>。
